<div id="aggregatePopup" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-80 flex items-center justify-center hidden">
    <div class="rounded p-6 w-full max-w-xl animate-popin backdrop-blur-md bg-neutral-400/5 border border-white/15">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-white flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa fa-compress text-orange-500" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Aggregate Old Metrics
        </h2>
        <div class="text-white mb-4">
            <p class="mb-3">This will aggregate old metrics (older than 31 days) into monthly averages to save database space.</p>
            <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 border border-neutral-700 rounded p-3 text-sm">
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>What will happen:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-neutral-300">
                    <li>Old detailed metrics will be grouped by month</li>
